Ok, this is the third time I posting this post, so I'm going to be very short about it. Its 12:17 am and I am in a very very bad mood.

I had lots of arguments about this US VS Canada thing but I don't want to further this flame war, so I'll keep them to myself. The next person to post a pointless OOC will get severely punished, I am not kidding. If you want OOC, go to the damn message board. I made it for a reason.

::Zardus::

Zardus nods, walking into the Iron Fist and heading for the conference room. "I'll show the status once we're in the conference room. Its easier with the aid of hologram projectors."

While he walks, his comm answers a few messages, though none were heard externally. "Yes, you may, Punch," he replies to Punch and then goes on to reply to Dark One.

"Judging from your performance in the last battle, a raise that generous isn't really in order right now. However, I will raise it by 40 kilograms, and maybe more if your team improves. Your payment right now will be waiting for you in storage room 7. You may use Lab 8 in the Iron Fist for upgrades."

With that he enters the conference room, sitting down and motioning for Daemos to do the same.
